{"tid":1728330,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[攬炒]緊握經濟春袋，你我有責","createTime":"2019-11-16T22:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T04:17:09.000Z","uid":34816,"like":20,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"3c2dfb86b86a40ab4002df197c5a111a9d80413f","tid":1728330,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:29:04.000Z","msg":"呢兩日睇左咁多分化po，加上局勢急速變化，方向上係咪有d迷惘呢，唔洗怕！我地只需要記住兩個字即可：<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">攬炒！</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家有無見過一篇兩個月前既文許，係講緊點樣達至經濟攬炒，在此借用重貼一下：<br />\n<br />\n[攬炒焦土經濟學]只要事件持續到年尾 死亡旋渦就會形成<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1552621\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1552621</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n個死亡旋渦我地已經接近完成！呢個亦係港共乃至中共既最大春袋！<br />\n<br />\n佢地而家真係好撚急想平息件事，甚至到左亂石投藥既階段，出老解試水溫咁低招都出埋了。<br />\n<br />\n我地一定要堅持落去，好快就到12月聖誕，然後直落就係新年，只要成功引爆香港經濟，中共無可能獨善其用，一定會受到重創甚至崩潰，配合埋貿易戰，呢個係消滅成個中共既最好時機。<br />\n<br />\n你願意攬炒嗎？<br />\n反正我願意了。"},{"pid":"1513df771036f29ab87d54d6c460a3a028fb7607","tid":1728330,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />港共想平息？食屎啦，叫黑警填命再講"},{"pid":"c77256654f3754a2e928ca6bd8c47e02e7dd07e2","tid":1728330,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:32:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcb05e28a33a837eede690b63f583def7991f672","tid":1728330,"uid":34816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T22:44:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"623f12574cffda2cc529bb9ebb7b2b6ce55405de","tid":172